## 3. The Sigma Stack

ΣBUS defines a seven-layer stack. Unlike OSI, these layers are not numbered to suggest
correspondence with OSI — they are an independent model for autonomous agent systems.

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│  L7  ACTION & VERIFICATION                                          │
│      Physical or digital actuation. AHK · PyAutoGUI · AT-SPI       │
│      Post-action verification loop. Outcome ΣFrames emitted.       │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  L6  AGENTS & POLICY                                                │
│      LLM inference tiers. CrewAI / LangGraph crews.                │
│      Policy engine. Human override gate (inalienable).             │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  L5  CONTEXT & MATRIX                                               │
│      ΣMatrix — in-memory graph (networkx) + SQLite persistence.    │
│      World model slices. Semantic query. Cross-source correlation. │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  L4  SEMANTIC NORMALIZATION                                         │
│      OmniParser (GUI) · NMEA parser · SigMF (SDR) · AIS decoder   │
│      Transaction parsers. Domain parsers → typed entities/events.  │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  L3  METADATA & IDENTITY                                            │
│      AID — Agent Identity Descriptor.                              │
│      ΣCard — stream registration. ΣTags — metadata vocabulary.    │
│      Trust · provenance · retention · ACL · anomaly scoring.      │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  L2  TRANSPORT & ENVELOPE                                           │
│      NATS JetStream (primary). asyncio queues (fallback).          │
│      ΣFrame wire format. SemanticEnvelope. Ed25519 signing.        │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  L1  CAPTURE                                                        │
│      mss (screenshots). UI Automation tree. NMEA/0183 serial.      │
│      SDR IQ. AIS over UDP. Logs. Camera frames.                    │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│  L0  SUBSTRATE                                                      │
│      Hardware. Operating system. Screens. Sensors. RF spectrum.    │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

Data flows **upward** from L0 to L6. Commands flow **downward** from L6 to L7.
The ΣBUS core (this document) governs L2 through L4.

