## 4. Path Naming Convention

Every data item in ΣBUS is addressed by a fully-qualified, hierarchical path.

### 4.1 Grammar

```
path         ::= platform "." domain "." entity "." attribute
platform     ::= identifier                    # vessel name, host ID
domain       ::= identifier                    # nav | engine | power | comms | agent | meta | desktop | rf
entity       ::= identifier ("." identifier)*  # may be nested
attribute    ::= identifier                    # leaf — always a scalar or typed compound

identifier   ::= [a-z0-9_]+                    # lowercase, underscores only
```

### 4.2 Rules

1. **Always fully qualified.** No short names or aliases on the bus.
2. **Lowercase, dots as separators, underscores within segments.**
3. **Leaf nodes are attributes, never containers.** `wibo835.nav.position` is not a valid path; `wibo835.nav.position.gps_primary.lat` is.
4. `meta.*` is reserved for system self-description.
5. `agent.*` is reserved for agent-generated data. Consumers must treat it as `data_class: "inferred"`.
6. Raw sensor paths never share a path prefix with derived data.
7. Command paths always live under `{platform}.cmd.*`.

### 4.3 Domain Vocabulary

| Domain | Description | Examples |
|---|---|---|
| `nav` | Navigation and position | `nav.position.gps_primary.lat`, `nav.ais.target_{mmsi}.cpa` |
| `engine` | Propulsion systems | `engine.port.rpm`, `engine.port.temp_coolant` |
| `power` | Electrical systems | `power.bank_a.voltage`, `power.solar.current` |
| `comms` | Communications | `comms.hf.js8call.last_rx`, `comms.vhf.channel` |
| `agent` | Agent-generated state | `agent.nav_agent.state`, `agent.nav_agent.last_decision` |
| `meta` | System self-description | `meta.stream.health`, `meta.world_model.version` |
| `desktop` | GUI / screen streams | `desktop.monitor.0.state`, `desktop.window.opencpn.state` |
| `rf` | Radio / SDR streams | `rf.sdr.iq.channel_0`, `rf.burst.detected` |
| `cmd` | Commands (write paths) | `cmd.autopilot.heading`, `cmd.engine.throttle` |

### 4.4 Wibo 835 Example Paths

```
wibo835.nav.position.gps_primary.lat
wibo835.nav.position.gps_primary.lon
wibo835.nav.position.gps_primary.trust
wibo835.nav.ais.target_987654321.cpa
wibo835.nav.ais.target_987654321.tcpa
wibo835.nav.ais.target_987654321.bearing
wibo835.engine.port.rpm
wibo835.engine.port.temp_coolant
wibo835.engine.port.temp_exhaust
wibo835.engine.port.oil_pressure
wibo835.power.bank_a.voltage
wibo835.power.bank_a.current
wibo835.power.bank_a.soc_pct
